    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>Does it have to be specifically an InputStreamReader?  How about using <a href=\"http://java.sun.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/io/StringReader.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">StringReader</a>?</p>\n\n<p>Otherwise, you could use <a href=\"http://java.sun.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/io/StringBufferInputStream.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">StringBufferInputStream</a>, but it's deprecated because of character conversion issues (which is why you should prefer StringReader).</p>\n"
