      "body" : "<a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/io/ByteArrayInputStream.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><code>ByteArrayInputStream </code></a>: <b>Since:</b>  JDK1.0   There’s not the slightest reason to assume that this class is “since Java 1.4”. That wrong version number is especially weird as Java 1.4 introduced <code>NIO</code> and it makes little sense to introduce an API and its conceptional successor within the same version."
