    "body" : "<p><a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/io/ByteArrayInputStream.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">ByteArrayInputStream</a> also does the trick:</p>\n\n<pre><code>InputStream is = new ByteArrayInputStream( myString.getBytes( charset ) );\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Then convert to reader:</p>\n\n<pre><code>InputStreamReader reader = new InputStreamReader(is);\n</code></pre>\n"
