    "body" : "<p>I also found the apache commons <code>IOUtils</code> class , so : </p>\n\n<pre><code>InputStreamReader isr = new InputStreamReader(IOUtils.toInputStream(myString));\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 1511094,
      "reputation" : 800,
      "user_id" : 1413206,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/2f4c82307b3bc357061cd73a55f52d14?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "Fai Ng",
